ygData.messageBody:
Hello All ,
I remember seeing a discussion going on about, where to purchase the
Water Breathing song , and its effect is obvious, but my question is , is it
useful ? Are there any dungeons that are completely under water? things like
that really interest me , someplace that almost no one goes to. If anyone
knows it would be greatly appreciated .
P.S. - if you don't want to spoil it for others , e-mail is a-ok.
Ulilien of Tunare
